item.dc:creator: @jmull jmull
item.description:
@jmull wrote:

[quote=“Dr. Dre, post:2, topic:6016”][quote author=jmull link=topic=8108.msg86502#msg86502 date=1153772948]
you dont have to edit the firewall since there wont be any incoming activity without outgoing activity. Only if you’re hosting should you have to port forward. but of course there are some firewalls that are exceptions to that but I seriously doubt you’ll need to change any firewalll settings.

as for connectiong. try multiple servers, if it doesnt work then you know there’s a problem. you can try logging into my server for testing (is up and you can connect).
IP of my server: firstmilkman.no-ip.org
[/quote]

I had to allow that port for it to work for me. :P[/quote]

I didnt have to do anyhting to play, only to host.
